org.apache.flex.compiler.asdoc

Interface IASDocBundleDelegate


  • public interface IASDocBundleDelegate
    Delegate interface used by ASProject to delegate queries of the ASDoc bundle files to clients.

    ASDoc bundles are resource bundle SWCs that contain DITA files with localized ASDoc information.

    • Field Summary

      Fields

      A default implementation of IASDocBundleDelegate.

    • Method Detail

      • getComment

        IASDocComment getComment(IDocumentableDefinition definition,
                       String containingSWCFileName)
        Retrieves the localized IASDocComment for the specified IDocumentableDefinition in the specified SWC file.
        Parameters:
        definition - The IDocumentableDefinition whose comment is to be returned.
        containingSWCFileName - The file name of the SWC containing the specified definition.
        Returns:
        A IASDocComment for the specified definition in the specified SWC file, localized for the current locale of the JVM, or null if there is no comment.
